---
// Four-layer animated case-study background.
// - .bg__base holds the per-project brand-colour gradient and slides horizontally.
// - .bg__fg-radial: white radial wash, top-centre origin. Animated to
//   transparent during page transitions.
// - .bg__fg-linear: white linear wash, top→bottom. Animated to fully
//   opaque during page transitions.
// Splitting the two washes into separate elements lets the page-wipe
// animate each layer's gradient-stop alphas independently via WAAPI.
// Brand colours come in via the `--brand-primary` / `--brand-secondary`
// CSS custom properties (declared as @property tokens in _tokens.scss).
// Project pages set them inline on <body> in BaseLayout so they're
// inherited globally; the homepage observer writes them to :root.
---
<div class="bg" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="bg__base" transition:persist="bg-base"></div>
  <div class="bg__fg-radial" transition:persist="bg-fg-radial"></div>
  <div class="bg__fg-linear" transition:persist="bg-fg-linear"></div>
</div>
